# Testing

- Pick the lowest layer that proves the behavior.
- Use package tests for parsing, rendering, and pure logic.
- Use GPU integration tests only for behavior requiring DCGM/hardware.
- Use Docker and Kubernetes e2e tests only when runtime/deployment behavior is
  involved and prerequisites exist.
- Document unavailable prerequisites instead of claiming a skipped gate passed.
